.Dd November 18, 2018
.Dt HP-SMTPD 1
.Os hp-tools
.Sh NAME
.Nm hp-smtpd
.Nd smtp daemon
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Cm tcpserver Ar 0 Ar 25 Nm
.Sh DESCRIPTION
.Nm
pretends behaviour of qmail smtpd and stores all incoming messages to the
.Ev MAILDIR .
.Sh ENVIRONMENT
.Bl -tag -width Ds
.It Ev HOSTNAME
sets the hostname used in greeting message and
.Ic helo ,
.Ic ehlo
and
.Ic quit
replies.
It uses
.Nm
if
.Ev HOSTNAME
is not set.
.It Ev MAILDIR
sets the location of the maildir.
This environment variable is mandatory.
.El
.Sh SEE ALSO
.Xr tcpserver 1 .
